OL,3,CUS issues arrest warrant against
OL,4,CIndia's richest billionaire for fraud
OL,6,FWords by Sanjay Jha, ITV News Producer
OL,7,Fin New Delhi
OL,9,FA New York court has indicted and
OL,10,Fissued an arrest warrant against
OL,11,FGautam Adani - Asia's richest
OL,12,Fbillionaire.
OL,14,FThe business tycoon has interests
OL,15,Franging from ports and airports to
OL,16,Frenewable energy in India and around
OL,17,Fthe world.
