OL,3,CUS issues arrest warrant against
OL,4,CIndia's richest billionaire for fraud
OL,6,FGautam Adani, who India's opposition
OL,7,Fcalls a close ally of Prime Minister
OL,8,FNarendra Modi, has been accused of
OL,9,Fconspiring to pay hundreds of millions
OL,10,Fof dollars to bribe Indian government
OL,11,Fofficials to win solar energy
OL,12,Fcontracts.
OL,14,FThe case alleges Mr Adani's company,
OL,15,FAdani Green Energy Ltd and another
OL,16,Ffirm secured a lucrative deal to sell
OL,17,F12 gigawatts of solar power to the
OL,18,FIndian government - enough to power
OL,19,Fmillions of homes and businesses.
