OL,3,CUS issues arrest warrant against
OL,4,CIndia's richest billionaire for fraud
OL,6,FProsecutors say Adani, his nephew
OL,7,FSagar Adani, and six other associates,
OL,8,Fpresented the project as promising to
OL,9,FWall Street investors, who invested
OL,10,Fbillions into the project over five
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, back in India, they were
OL,14,Faccused of arranging or paying $265
OL,15,Fmillion in bribes to Indian officials
OL,16,Fto secure billions of dollars worth of
OL,17,Fcontracts and financing.
