OL,3,CUS issues arrest warrant against
OL,4,CIndia's richest billionaire for fraud
OL,6,FIt further alleges that "on several
OL,7,Foccasions, Gautam S. Adani personally
OL,8,Fmet with an Indian government official
OL,9,Fto advance the bribery scheme" and
OL,10,Fclaims to have electronic and mobile
OL,11,Fphone evidence of this.
OL,13,FThe criminal charges, filed on
OL,14,FWednesday in New York, are the latest
OL,15,Fblow to the 62-year-old Mr Adani,
OL,16,Fwhose stock prices crashed after the
OL,17,Fnews was released.
