OL,3,CUS issues arrest warrant against
OL,4,CIndia's richest billionaire for fraud
OL,6,FImmediately following the indictment,
OL,7,FAdani Green Energy announced it would
OL,8,Fnot proceed with a $600 million bond
OL,9,Foffering.
OL,11,FThe group called the allegations
OL,12,Fbaseless and stated that "possible
OL,13,Flegal recourse will be sought."
OL,15,FPreviously, US short-seller Hindenburg
OL,16,FResearch published a report accusing
OL,17,Fthe Adani Group of brazen stock
OL,18,Fmanipulation and accounting fraud, but
OL,19,Fthis indictment represents the biggest
OL,20,Fsetback for the group so far.
